      "title": "📬 Staff Soccer Game Rooter Bus",
      "summary": "Hello Panthers! Get ready—our upcoming Staff Soccer Showdown is almost here!",
      "date": "2026-05-11",
      "author": "Lisa Walters",
      "url": "https://www.parentsquare.com/feeds/80165994",
      "pinned": false,
      "body": "<p style=\"margin:0in;font-size:15px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:white !important;vertical-align:baseline;\"><span style=\"border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-size:24px;line-height:inherit;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;color:rgb(0, 96, 128);\">Hello Panthers! Get ready—our upcoming Staff Soccer Showdown is almost here! </span></p><p style=\"margin:0in;font-size:15px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:white !important;vertical-align:baseline;\"><span style=\"border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-size:24px;line-height:inherit;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;color:rgb(0, 96, 128);\">Your PVHS staff will be taking on the staff from Santa Maria High School in an exciting matchup, and we want YOU there to cheer us on!</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in;font-size:15px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:white !important;vertical-align:baseline;\"><span style=\"border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-size:24px;line-height:inherit;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;color:rgb(0, 96, 128);\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin:0in;font-size:15px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:white !important;vertical-align:baseline;\"><span style=\"border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-size:24px;line-height:inherit;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;color:rgb(0, 96, 128);\">We’ll have a one-way rooter bus leaving PV stadium parking lot at 4:30 PM, so make sure you’re there by 4:15 PM sharp. Spots are limited, so sign up with Ms. Perez during lunch or after school. Her office is located right next to the Dean’s office.</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in;font-size:15px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:white !important;vertical-align:baseline;\"><span style=\"border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-size:24px;line-height:inherit;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;color:rgb(0, 96, 128);\">The deadline to sign up is next Wednesday, May 13th.</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in;font-size:15px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-size:24px;line-height:inherit;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;color:rgb(0, 96, 128);\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin:0in;font-size:15px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-size:24px;line-height:inherit;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;color:rgb(0, 96, 128);\">Come out, bring the energy, and help us represent PV loud and proud. Go Panthers! </span></p><p style=\"margin:0in;font-size:15px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-size:24px;line-height:inherit;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;color:rgb(0, 96, 128);\"><span style=\"border:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\">- Mr. Basulto, Dean of Students</span></span></p>",
