      "id": "79978456",
      "title": "🎓 Class of 2026 College Acceptance Survey",
      "summary": "Hey Panthers! If you applied to a four-year university, we want to hear from you!",
      "date": "2026-05-08",
      "author": "Melani Mederos",
      "url": "https://www.parentsquare.com/feeds/79978456",
      "pinned": false,
      "body": "<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size:22px;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Hey Panthers!<br><br>If you applied to a four-year university, we want to hear from you! Please scan the QR Code below and take our survey. Your responses will be featured in the Senior Awards Night Program. If you've committed to a university, please make sure to indicate which one. <br><br><strong>The last day to submit the survey is Wednesday, May 13th.<br></strong><br>Senior Awards Night is Tuesday, May 19th in the PVHS Gym starting at 5:30 p.m. This event is invitation only, and invitations were sent in the mail today! Please be on the lookout for your postcard. There will also be a separate ParentSquare sent for the attendees and their families. <br><br>We know May is a busy month, but we want to be sure and celebrate you for all of your hard work!<br><br>Thank you for taking the survey!<br><br>If you have any questions, please see Mrs. Mederos in the College &amp; Career Center.<br></span> </span><img src=\"https://posts.parentsquare.com/inline_images_606faa76c3e70fec_1778276581307-College+Acceptance+Survey+2026.png\" style=\"width:562px;display:block;vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\">\n</div><br><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">Have a great weekend, Panthers!</span>",
