      "body": "<span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">May is Mental Health Awareness Month, and the Wellness Center is excited to share a full calendar of activities, support, and connection opportunities for students.</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Monthly Highlights:</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Share &amp; Care Club Meetings - Held regularly (note: May 26 meeting cancelled).</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Peer Leaders Meeting - @ Lunch on May 6.</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Words of Encouragement Rock Painting - @ Lunch on May 7.</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Salty &amp; Sweet DIY Salt Scrub Workshop - @ Lunch on May 14.</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Mental Health Awareness Week - May 18-22</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Dress Up Day: Wear Green - May 20 to show support for mental health awareness.</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Cloud Dough Workshop - @ Lunch on May 18.</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Mental Health Resource Fair - @ Lunch on May 22.</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Mental Health Workshop (Hosted by CAPSLO) - @ Lunch on May 27.</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">Important Dates &amp; Closures:</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">May 8: District Wellness Meeting @ 12:30 PM - Wellness Center Closed</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);display:inline !important;float:none;\">May 26: Wellness Center Closed (9:30 AM- 4:30 PM)</span><br style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(42, 45, 47);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);di