      "url": "https://www.parentsquare.com/feeds/78892577",
      "pinned": false,
      "body": "<h2>FINAL REMINDER: Future Panther Night is TOMORROW (Wed 4/29)! (Note Time Change)</h2>We are officially less than 24 hours away from welcoming our newest Panthers! Please take note of a <strong>slight update to our schedule</strong> to ensure you don’t miss our exciting opening ceremonies.<br><h3>⏰ Updated Schedule:</h3><ul>\n<li>\n<strong>5:30 PM:</strong> Doors Open (Panther Gym)</li>\n<li>\n<strong>5:45 PM:</strong> <strong>Live Performances Begin!</strong>\n</li>\n</ul>Make sure to arrive by <strong>5:30 PM</strong> to grab a seat before our student performers take the floor to kick off the night with a bang!<br><br><h3>🎒 What’s in Store for You?</h3>Once the performances conclude, the floor is yours! This is the ultimate \"one-stop shop\" for everything Pioneer Valley:<br><ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Club &amp; Team Showcase:</strong> From the soccer field to the robotics lab, come \"shop\" for the activities that make high school memorable.</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Meet Your Coaches &amp; Teachers:</strong> Get face-to-face time with the mentors who will support your student over the next four years.</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Essential Info:</strong> Get the final word on what you need for a successful transition this fall.</li>\n</ul><h3>📍 Location Recap</h3><strong>Where:</strong> The Panther Gym<br><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, April 29th @ 5:30 PM- 7:00PM<br>We’ve put in the work to make this a fun, engaging, and informative night for the whole family. We can't wait to see the gym filled with the energy of our future Class of 2030!<br><strong>See you tomorrow night! Go Panthers! 🐾</strong>",
